commandLineTool

Class Launch

  • java.lang.Object
    • commandLineTool.Launch

  • public class Launch
extends java.lang.Object
    Command-line-user-interface. The class contains all the functions that are used for the CLUI. The help-String is stored in this class as well.
    Author:
    maxspahn, jeremyaugot
